m_q.target_metric: count of nations with zero silver medals

format_notes: Rank column contains Int64 values with possible ties (same rank appears multiple times)
Nation column contains country name with IOC code in parentheses
All medal count columns are Int64 type

constraints: Silver column must be non-negative integer
Total should equal Gold + Silver + Bronze
All nations in table should have at least one medal (Total >= 1)
